prompt: Create a professional medical illustration showing the mesenteric vascular anatomy from an anterior view. Use red for arteries with arrows flowing AWAY from the aorta toward the intestines. Include clear labels. The aorta runs vertically on the LEFT side of the image, with branches extending to the RIGHT. Clean educational style with white background, suitable for a surgical textbook. High-quality medical illustration.
